summary: As a Finnish person who grew up with Moomin, it’s amazing for me to see your art of the characters! You do a very good job at...
question: As a Finnish person who grew up with Moomin, it’s amazing for me to see your art of the characters! You do a very good job at capturing their personalities, and it looks very clean. I especially love the way you draw Too-Ticky (it feels strange to write her name in English), who by the way is based off of Tove Jansson’s (the author of the original Moomin books&comics) partner! This was always exciting to me as a closeted gay myself; I don’t know how you identify, but you may find this cool!
answer:
I’m really glad you enjoy my art!  and I’m happy to hear I do the characters justice! It really is a wonderfull series and I’m happy to finally get into, n also a good excuse to learn about Finnish culture and folklore!

 And yeah… im a big lesbian so its nice to see too ticky being fat butch rights… i love her so much
